OL,3,CGovernment launches baby loss
OL,4,Ccertificate to 'recognise grief of
OL,5,Cparents'
OL,7,FBabies stillborn before 24 weeks do
OL,8,Fnot need to be officially registered,
OL,9,Fleaving some parents feeling ignored
OL,11,FA baby loss certificate scheme
OL,12,Fdesigned to recognise the grief of
OL,13,Fparents who lose a baby early in a
OL,14,Fpregnancy has been launched.
OL,16,FThe voluntary scheme offers those who
OL,17,Fexperience a loss pre-24 weeks'
OL,18,Fgestation a certificate to formally
OL,19,Frecognise the devastating impact.
