OL,7,FThe certificates will be available for
OL,8,Feither parent to access following a
OL,9,Floss under 24 weeks since September
OL,10,F2018, with the government planning to
OL,11,Fexpand eligibility in the near future.
OL,13,FOn a visit to a family bereavement
OL,14,Fcentre at the maternity unit, Maria
OL,15,FCaulfield, Minister for the Women's
OL,16,FHealth Strategy, said parents who lose
OL,17,Fa baby before 24 weeks can feel there
OL,18,Fis a "lack of recognition of that
OL,19,Fbaby".
