OL,7,FThe suite at St George's was
OL,8,Frefurbished in October after the
OL,9,Ffamily of a baby who died after birth
OL,10,Fraised more than #80,000 towards its
OL,11,Frenovation.
OL,13,FNot all hospitals have such
OL,14,Ffacilities, and Ms Caulfield was told
OL,15,Fby midwives on the visit that they
OL,16,Fshould be "standard" in maternity
OL,17,Funits.
