OL,7,F"Part of our pregnancy loss review is
OL,8,Fseeing how we can get that as a
OL,9,Fstandard facility in all maternity
OL,10,Funits.
OL,12,F"There's a number of things that we
OL,13,Fcan do, that will make a difference,
OL,14,Fbut that is on top of trying to reduce
OL,15,Fthe number of deaths from stillbirths
OL,16,Fand neonatal deaths in the first
OL,17,Fplace."
