OL,7,F"The pain of losing a baby before 24
OL,8,Fweeks is often made even worse for
OL,9,Fbereaved parents because there is no
OL,10,Fformal recognition of their experience.
OL,12,F"We're pleased that baby loss
OL,13,Fcertificates will now be available to
OL,14,Fprovide a degree of comfort for at
OL,15,Fleast some of those families."
OL,17,FBut Ms Abrahams said miscarriage
OL,18,Fremains a "largely hidden problem"
OL,19,Fbecause of a lack of government
OL,20,Fcommitment to gathering statistics on
OL,21,Fthe issue.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@^O]zD@KOUzD@bO]
