OL,7,F"We do believe, however, that more
OL,8,Fmust be done to formally record losses
OL,9,Fbefore 24 weeks," she continued.
OL,11,F"We cannot begin to tackle the wider
OL,12,Fproblem of baby loss without a
OL,13,Fgovernment commitment to gather and
OL,14,Frecord UK-wide miscarriage statistics.
OL,16,F"Without data, miscarriage remains a
OL,17,Flargely hidden problem and isn't
OL,18,Fprioritised, despite the tens of
OL,19,Fthousands of families affected by it
OL,20,Fevery year."
